title: Harvey Mandel - [1995] The Mercury Years (FLAC)
description:
Harvey Mandel - The Mercury Years (FLAC)
Release Date: 1995


Double-CD reissue repackages the entire contents of his first three LPs (1968's Cristo Redentor, 1969's Righteous, 1970's Games Guitars Play) in their original track sequence, with extensive, informative liner notes. (Liner notes booklet included in torrent)
